ionic Beaver)\r\n**Release or commit:** libglfw3-wayland/focal,now 3.3.2-1 amd64\r\n**Error messages:** (none) Segmentation Fault\r\n**Call stack:**\r\nI was not able to load debug symbols for the wayland library, but I have made a minimal example app which reproduces the issue in my environment. If I have time, I will try to compile `libglfw3-wayland` from scratch and get the full stack trace.\r\n\r\nHere is the example app. It just creates a blank full screen window, and will iconify when the key press \"M\" is detected.\r\n\r\n```\r\n#include <GLFW/glfw3.h>\r\n\r\n#include <iostream>\r\n\r\nusing namespace std;\r\n\r\nbool s_quit = false;\r\n\r\nvoid keyCallback(GLFWwindow* window, int key, int scancode, int action, int mods)\r\n{\r\n    if (key == GLFW_KEY_M && action == GLFW_PRESS)\r\n    {\r\n        glfwIconifyWindow(window);\r\n    }\r\n    if (key == GLFW_KEY_Q && action == GLFW_PRESS)\r\n    {\r\n        s_quit = true;\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\nint main()\r\n{\r\n    glfwInit();\r\n    glfwWindowHint(GLFW_VISIBLE, GLFW_TRUE);\r\n    GLFWwindow* window = glfwCreateWindow(640, 480, \"My Title\", glfwGetPrimaryMonitor(), nullptr);\r\n    if (!window)\r\n    {\r\n        cerr << \"Can't create window!\" << endl;\r\n        return 1;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    glfwSetKeyCallback(window, keyCallback);\r\n\r\n    while (!s_quit)\r\n    {\r\n        glfwWaitEvents();\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    glfwDestroyWindow(window);\r\n    glfwTerminate();\r\n\r\n    return 0;\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n**Steps to reproduce:**\r\n1. Start this app using `libglfw3-wayland` in a Wayland session\r\n2. Press M on the keyboard\r\n\r\n**Expected Behaviour:**\r\nThe app iconifies and continues to function\r\n\r\n**Actual Behaviour:**\r\nThe app crashes with a Segmentation Fault\r\n```\r\nThread 1 (Thread 0x7ffff79cd300 (LWP 18657)):\r\n#0  0x00007ffff7f5e500 in ?? () from /lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libglfw.so.3\r\nNo symbol table info available.\r\n#1  0x00007ffff7f678f8 in ?? () from /lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libglfw.so.3\r\nNo symbol table info available.\r\n#2  0x0000555555555375 in main () at /home/waris/dev/glfw-test/main.cpp:36\r\n        window = 0x555555591d20\r\n```\r\n\r\nLet me know if you need more info.","closed_by":{"login":"elmindreda","id":133714,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEzMzcxNA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/133714?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda","html_url":"https://github.com/elmindreda","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/glfw/glfw/issues/1704/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/glfw/glfw/issues/1704/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed"}